Package org.yamcs.cmdhistory

Interface CommandHistoryPublisher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StreamCommandHistoryPublisher
    public interface CommandHistoryPublisher
    Used by the commanding applications to save commands and commands acknowledgements into a history.

      • ACK_SENT_CNAME_PREFIX

        static final String ACK_SENT_CNAME_PREFIX
        Used by the links to add entries in the command history when the command has been sent via the link.

        The entries will be <ACK_SENT_CNAME_PREFIX>_Status and <ACK_SENT_CNAME_PREFIX>_Time

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • publishAck

        default void publishAck​(Commanding.CommandId cmdId,
                        String key,
                        long time,
                        CommandHistoryPublisher.AckStatus state,
                        String message)
        Publish an acknowledgement status to the command history.

        Three entries (corresponding to command history columns) are created:

        • key_Time
        • key_Status
        • key_Message
        Parameters:
        cmdId -
